title: ‘The Challenge: Ride or Dies’ Episode 2 With Nany | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
In her podcast debut, Nany Gonzalez joins Johnny to tell the story of how Team Banany came to be, talk about her conflict with Turbo and the rookies' risky strategy, break down the daily challenge and elimination in Episode 2, and so much more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Nany Gonzalez
Producer: Sasha Ashall
